  m_Name: Speech_MrNorrmalm_Opening
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ClientSpeech
  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: adb7bea0237e1aa4bb638029bc97dad1, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "Man, I don\u2019t get to talk to a cutie like you that often\u2026
    I bet you\u2019re single, huh? Well, it\u2019s not like you\u2019ve mentioned
    any boyfriend\u2026 Right, the woman I used to date? We just fell out of love\u2026
    The poly thing wasn\u2019t part of it, I\u2019d met her parents and everything.
    Good god, I hate cats. They\u2019re like little demons who shit on everything,
    do absolutely jack shit, and get praised just for existing. Since when did they
    get so great? But seriously, it\u2019s not like women are wired to have more
    partners, right?"
